verbose_text: The expression of collagen type I (collagen I), alpha-smooth muscle actin (alpha-SMA), TGF-beta1, SMAD3, SMAD7, hypoxia inducible factor 1 alpha (HIF-1alpha), and vascular endothelial grow factor (VEGF) were assessed by immunohistochemistry and quantitative real-time polymerase chain (RT-qPCR) reaction.
